'''瑞典中央銀行紀念阿爾弗雷德·諾貝爾經濟學獎'''（{{lang-sv|Sveriges riksbanks pris i ekonomisk vetenskap till Alfred Nobels minne}}；{{lang-en|The Sveriges Riksbank Prize in Economic Sciences in Memory of Alfred Nobel}}），通常稱為「諾貝爾經濟學獎」<ref>{{cite book|first=John A.|last=Hird.|title=Power, Knowledge, and Politics|year=2005|publisher=Georgetown University Press|isbn=978-1-58901-048-2|page=33|quote=the Bank of Sweden Prize in Economic Sciences in Memory of Alfred Nobel, commonly referred to as the Nobel Prize in Economics, was awarded to economists beginning in 1969.|oclc=231997210|series=American governance and public policy}}</ref><ref name="auto">{{cite journal|first=Bernard|last=Guerrien|authorlink=Bernard Guerrien|title=A science too human? Economics|date=2004-03-15|journal=Post-autistic economics review|url=http://www.paecon.net/PAEReview/issue24/Guerrien24.htm|issue=4|quote=commonly called the "Nobel prize for economics" although from this it does not follow that it is one|access-date=2014-11-23|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924063225/http://www.paecon.net/PAEReview/issue24/Guerrien24.htm|dead-url=yes}}</ref>（部分人反對此一通稱）<ref>{{cite web | title = Maybe economics doesn't deserve its own Nobel Prize | author = Kevin Hartnett | publisher = [[Boston_Globe|Boston Globe]] | date = 2013-10-15 | url = http://www.boston.com/bostonglobe/ideas/brainiac/2013/10/maybe_economics.html | accessdate = 2014-10-27 | archive-date = 2014-10-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141027191008/http://www.boston.com/bostonglobe/ideas/brainiac/2013/10/maybe_economics.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="auto"/><ref>{{cite web | title = The Beauty (Pageant?) of Economics | author = Ronald A. Wirtz | publisher = [[Federal_Reserve_Bank_of_Minneapolis|Federal Reserve Bank of Minneapolis]] | date = 1999-12-01 | accessdate = 2014-10-27 }}</ref>。經濟學獎屬於[[諾貝爾基金會|諾貝爾基金會]]專屬之「[[诺贝尔奖|諾貝爾獎]]」[[商標|商標]]中的「一種諾貝爾獎」<ref>{{cite web | title = Organization Structure: Spreading Information About the Nobel Prize | url = http://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_organizations/org_structure.html | publisher = [[The_Nobel_Foundation|The Nobel Foundation]] | accessdate = 2014-11-26 | archive-date = 2014-10-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141016140216/http://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_organizations/org_structure.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Legal Notice | publisher = [[The_Nobel_Foundation|The Nobel Foundation]] | url = http://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_organizations/nobelmedia/nobelprize_org/copyright/legal_notice.pdf | accessdate = 2014-11-26 | archive-date = 2014-10-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141007204038/http://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_organizations/nobelmedia/nobelprize_org/copyright/legal_notice.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = NOBEL PRIZE | publisher = [[USPTO|USPTO]] | url = http://tmsearch.uspto.gov/bin/showfield?f=doc&state=4804:w3n2l2.2.8 | accessdate = 2014-10-27 | archive-date = 2017-10-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171009195206/http://tmsearch.uspto.gov/bin/showfield?f=doc&state=4804:w3n2l2.2.8 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，是表彰[[经济学|经济学]]领域杰出研究者的奖项，被广泛认为是经济学的最高獎<ref name="EB-NP">{{cite web|title=Nobel Prize|publisher=[[Encyclopædia_Britannica|Encyclopædia Britannica]]|year=2007|url=http://www.britannica.com/eb/article-9056008|accessdate=2007-11-14|quote=An additional award, the Sveriges Riksbank Prize in Economic Sciences in Memory of [[Alfred_Nobel|Alfred Nobel]], was established in 1968 by the Bank of Sweden and was first awarded in 1969. Thus, its winners are announced with the Nobel Prize recipients, and the Prize in Economic Sciences is presented at the Nobel Prize Award Ceremony.|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071214162150/http://www.britannica.com/eb/article-9056008|archivedate=2007-12-14}}</ref>。儘管此獎項並不屬於[[阿爾弗雷德·諾貝爾|諾貝爾]]遺囑中所提到的5大獎項，但一般認爲此獎項與5大獎項地位相同，并與它們在同一典禮上頒授<ref name="EB-NP"/>。

經濟學獎是由[[瑞典中央銀行|瑞典中央銀行]]於其成立300週年（1668-1968）時所設立，並於1969年首次頒獎，由[[挪威|挪威]][[朗納·弗里施|朗納·弗里施]]、[[荷蘭|荷蘭]][[簡·丁伯根|簡·丁伯根]]共同獲得，獲獎緣由是他們“爲經濟分析中動態模型的發展和應用做出了傑出的貢獻”<ref name="bank-estab" /><ref name=Tinbergen>[http://www.britannica.com/ebc/article-9380801 "Jan Tinbergen"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.britannica.com/ebc/article-9380801 |date=20071203025802 }}（2007）, in ''[[Encyclopædia_Britannica|Encyclopædia Britannica]]'', accessed November 16, 2007, from ''Encyclopædia Britannica Online'': <nowiki><http://www.britannica.com/eb/article-9380801{{dead link|date=2018年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}></nowiki>.</ref><ref name=Frisch>[http://www.britannica.com/ebc/article-9364984 "Ragnar Frisch"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.britannica.com/ebc/article-9364984 |date=20071202201407 }}（2007）, in ''[[Encyclopædia_Britannica|Encyclopædia Britannica]]'', accessed November 16, 2007, from ''Encyclopædia Britannica Online'': <nowiki><http://www.britannica.com/eb/article-9364984{{dead link|date=2018年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}></nowiki>.</ref>。

== 評選程序 ==
根據[[諾貝爾基金會|諾貝爾基金會]]的官方文件，諾貝爾經濟學獎由[[瑞典中央銀行|瑞典中央銀行]]在1968年（該銀行的300週年慶典）為紀念[[諾貝爾|諾貝爾]]而增設<ref name="EB-NP"/><ref>{{cite web|title=The Sveriges Riksbank Prize in Economic Sciences in Memory of Alfred Nobel|publisher=[[Sveriges_Riksbank|Sveriges Riksbank]]|url=http://www.riksbank.se/en/The-Riksbank/Economics-prize/|accessdate=2012-12-12|quote=Sveriges Riksbank’s Prize in Economic Sciences in Memory of Alfred Nobel was established in connection with the Riksbank’s 300th anniversary in 1968.|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130305075529/http://www.riksbank.se/en/The-Riksbank/Economics-prize/|archive-date=2013-03-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="NF-prizes">{{cite web|title=The Nobel Prize|publisher=[[The_Nobel_Foundation|The Nobel Foundation]]|url=http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/|accessdate=2007-11-07|quote=In 1968, Sveriges Riksbank established The Sveriges Riksbank Prize in Economic Sciences in Memory of Alfred Nobel, founder of the Nobel Prize.|archive-date=2013-06-22|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6HYcbFdx8?url=http://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="bank-estab">{{cite web|title=The Sveriges Riksbank Prize in Economic Sciences in Memory of Alfred Nobel|publisher=[[The_Nobel_Foundation|The Nobel Foundation]]|url=http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/economics/|accessdate=2007-11-07|quote=In 1968, Sveriges Riksbank（Sweden's central bank）established this Prize in memory of Alfred Nobel, founder of the Nobel Prize. The first Prize in Economics was awarded to Ragnar Frisch and Jan Tinbergen in 1969|archive-date=2013-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130531065737/http://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/economics/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此一獎項的評獎機構與'''[[诺贝尔物理学奖|诺贝尔物理学奖]]'''、'''[[諾貝爾化學獎|諾貝爾化學獎]]'''相同，均為[[瑞典皇家科學院|瑞典皇家科學院]]，在評選過程中亦採用一個與[[諾貝爾委員會|諾貝爾委員會]]組成、地位皆相似的“評選委員會”<ref name="statutes-econ"/><ref name=nomaw>[http://www.kva.se/KVA_Root/eng/awards/nobel/economy/nomination.asp "Nominating and Awarding"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.kva.se/KVA_Root/eng/awards/nobel/economy/nomination.asp |date=20061008021033 }}, in "Prize in Economic Sciences", ''[[Royal_Swedish_Academy_of_Sciences|Royal Swedish Academy of Sciences]]''. Retrieved November 17, 2007.</ref>。

每年9月，瑞典皇家科学院中由五人组成的评选委员会会向数千名科学家、学会成员和大学教授寄发邀请函，请他们提名下一年度的诺贝尔经济学奖的获奖候选人，瑞典皇家科学院院士与历届经济学奖得主也有提名权。<ref name="statutes-econ">{{cite web|title=Statutes for The Sveriges Riksbank Prize in Economic Sciences in Memory of Alfred Nobel approved by the Crown on the 19th day of December 1968|publisher=[[The_Nobel_Foundation|The Nobel Foundation]]|url=http://nobelprize.org/nobelfoundation/statutes-eco.html|accessdate=2007-10-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071020211408/http://nobelprize.org/nobelfoundation/statutes-eco.html|archivedate=2007-10-20|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

所有的提名和相关证词必须在来年1月1日之前寄到评选委员会。<ref name="selectionProcess">{{cite web|title=Nomination of the Laureates in Economics|publisher=[[The_Nobel_Foundation|The Nobel Foundation]]|url=http://nobelprize.org/nomination/economics/process.html|accessdate=2012-10-14|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716200421/http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/economics/nomination/|archivedate=2011-07-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>评选委员会和特别指定的专家会对提名进行审查。在9月结束前，评选委员会会选出“潜在的”获奖者，如果投票出现平局，评选委员会主席会投下决定性的一票。潜在的获奖者必须得到瑞典皇家科学院的批准。该院的社会科学家们会在10月中旬对诺贝尔经济学奖得主进行投票表决。<ref name="statutes-econ" /><ref name=nomaw/><ref name="kva-members">{{cite web|title=Members|publisher=[[Royal_Swedish_Academy_of_Sciences|Royal Swedish Academy of Sciences]]|url=http://www.kva.se/KVA_Root/eng/about/members/index.asp?br=ns&ver=6up|accessdate=2007-10-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080504225908/http://www.kva.se/KVA_Root/eng/about/members/index.asp?br=ns&ver=6up|archivedate=2008-05-04}}</ref>

诺贝尔经济学奖与其它五项诺贝尔奖遵循相同的规则，即：每届得奖人数不超过3人，得主在本年10月依旧健在，提名消息在50年内保密。<ref name="selectionProcess" />

诺贝尔奖颁奖典礼会在每年12月10日（[[诺贝尔|诺贝尔]]之忌辰）于[[斯德哥尔摩|斯德哥尔摩]]举行，经济学奖得主会与[[诺贝尔物理学奖|物理学奖]][[诺贝尔化学奖|化学奖]][[诺贝尔医学或生理学奖|医学或生理学奖]][[诺贝尔文学奖|文学奖]]的得主们一同接受由瑞典国王颁发的获奖证书、金质奖章和奖金支票。<ref name="EB-NP"/><ref name="NF-ceremonies">{{cite web|title=The Nobel Prize Award Ceremonies and Banquets|publisher=[[The_Nobel_Foundation|The Nobel Foundation]]|url=http://nobelprize.org/award_ceremonies/history.html|accessdate=2007-11-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071026084817/http://nobelprize.org/award_ceremonies/history.html|archivedate=2007-10-26|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

=== 資金來源 ===
諾貝爾經濟學獎的獎金與相關的評選、管理費用均由瑞典中央銀行“永久性”地全額撥付给[[诺贝尔基金会|诺贝尔基金会]]。<ref name="statutes-econ_quote2">{{cite web|title=Statutes for The Sveriges Riksbank Prize in Economic Sciences in Memory of Alfred Nobel approved by the Crown on the 19th day of December 1968|publisher=[[The_Nobel_Foundation|The Nobel Foundation]]|url=http://nobelprize.org/nobelfoundation/statutes-eco.html|accessdate=2007-11-16|quote=In celebration of the Tercentenary of [[Sveriges_Riksbank|Sveriges Riksbank]], the Bank has instituted a prize in economic sciences in memory of Alfred Nobel. ... The Prize shall be awarded annually to a person who has written a work on economic sciences of the eminent significance expressed in the will of Alfred Nobel drawn up on November 27, 1895. ... The Prize shall be awarded by the [[Royal_Swedish_Academy_of_Sciences|Royal Academy of Sciences]] in accordance with the rules governing the award of the Nobel Prizes instituted through his will.|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071020211408/http://nobelprize.org/nobelfoundation/statutes-eco.html|archivedate=2007-10-20|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

自2001年起，諾貝爾經濟學獎的獎金達到1000萬[[瑞典克朗|瑞典克朗]]（按照2014年11月匯率計算，約合136萬[[美元|美元]]），這與最初的五項諾貝爾獎的獎金數額相等。<ref name="econ-cash">{{cite web |title=The Prize Amount |publisher=[[The_Nobel_Foundation|The Nobel Foundation]] |url=http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/economics/amount.html |accessdate=2007-11-17 |archive-date=2013-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130402192714/http://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/economics/amount.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Lindbeck>[[Assar_Lindbeck|Assar Lindbeck]], [http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/economics/articles/lindbeck/index.html "The Sveriges Riksbank Prize in Economic Sciences in Memory of Alfred Nobel 1969–2006"] {{Wayback|url=http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/economics/articles/lindbeck/index.html |date=20130616085726 }}, ''nobelprize.org'', April 18, 1999. Retrieved November 11, 2007.</ref><ref name=RSAS>[http://www.kva.se/KVA_Root/eng/_news/detail.asp?NewsId=988 "The Prize in Economic Sciences 2007"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.kva.se/KVA_Root/eng/_news/detail.asp?NewsId=988 |date=20071114222806 }}, press release, [[Royal_Swedish_Academy_of_Sciences|Royal Swedish Academy of Sciences]], October 15, 2007. Retrieved November 16, 2007.</ref>

從2006年開始，瑞典中央銀行每年撥給[[諾貝爾基金會|諾貝爾基金會]]650萬[[瑞典克朗|瑞典克朗]]以支付該獎的評選與管理費用，并額外撥付100萬瑞典克朗以使此獎的相關訊息被諾貝爾基金會官網收錄。<ref name="bank-2006report">{{cite web|title=Årsredovidning 2006|publisher=[[Sveriges_Riksbank|Sveriges Riksbank]]|date=2007-03-29|url=http://www.riksbank.se/Upload/Dokument_riksbank/Kat_publicerat/Rapporter/2007/arsred_popvers_06_sve.pdf#page=68|format=PDF|accessdate=2013-09-15|quote=I posten ekonomipris ingår prissumman om 10 miljoner kronor samt administrationskostnader för detta pris om 6,5 miljoner kronor. Dessutom har bidrag givits till det interaktiva Internetmuseum som Nobelstiftelsen byggt upp. Bidraget avser täckande av kostnaden för information om ekonomipriset. Bidraget ska enligt avtal utbetalas årligen med 1 miljon kronor till och med 2008.|archive-date=2013-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130313070844/http://www.riksbank.se/Upload/Dokument_riksbank/Kat_publicerat/Rapporter/2007/arsred_popvers_06_sve.pdf#page=68|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

